esthaven Harbour Park Redevelopment Master Planning Team</li>\r\n	<li>St Kilda Subdivision – Cambridge</li>\r\n	<li>Oyster Capital Subdivisions</li>\r\n	<li>Northgate Industrial Park – Whangarei</li>\r\n	<li>Addison, McLennan Park, Anselmi Ridge Residential Subdivisions – McConnell Property Limited</li>\r\n	<li>Kawarau Falls Station – Queenstown</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last]\r\n\r\n<b>MARINE </b>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Onehunga Foreshore Restoration</li>\r\n	<li>Centreport – Wellington</li>\r\n	<li>Waterfront Auckland 20 year plan</li>\r\n	<li>ORAMS Heavy Lift System</li>\r\n	<li>ORAMS Expansion plans</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>AVIATION </b>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>AIAL Taxiway Lima</li>\r\n	<li>AIAL Airside and Terminal Projects</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_third_last]\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 350px;" valign="top"></td>\r\n<td style="width: 450px;" valign="top"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Vincent Baldwin | Director', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vincent-baldwin', '', '', '2014-10-25 03:54:30', '2014-10-25 03:54:30', '', 73, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/?page_id=189', 0, 'page', '', 0),
