(227, 1, '2013-03-26 02:47:14', '2013-03-26 02:47:14', 'In a challenging and uncertain civil construction environment Vince’s input helped to ensure that there were no cost surprise when it came time to  tender the project. \r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: medium;">– Donavin Wick - Property Project Manager Auckland International Airport Limited.</span>', 'Donavin Wick', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '227', '', '', '2013-10-14 03:34:42', '2013-10-14 03:34:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/access/?p=227', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(228, 1, '2013-08-15 03:10:32', '2013-08-15 03:10:32', '&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>When planning the delivery of Quad 5, Auckland Airport’s first speculative commercial office building in a number of years; and the headquarters of the airport’s management team, it was imperative that the end product was an outstanding facility and a financial success.\r\n\r\nJohn Giles, as the project Quantity Surveyor, was integral in ensuring both goals were achieved. Over the two year life of the project John was an exceptional team member who consistently delivered high quality and reliable advice and deliverables. We’d welcome the opportunity to work with John in the future.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>Donavin Wick</strong> ǀ Property Project Manager\r\n<strong>Auckland International Airport Limited</strong>\r\n<blockquote>Vince was an exceptional Commercial Manager, his work was of the highest standard and accuracy. He is a highly motivated individual willing to go that extra length to ensure the contract is successful.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>Tony Webb</strong> ǀ Director\r\n<strong>Pragmatix Limited</strong>\r\n<blockquote>I have worked with Greg on a number of projects over the years and he has always been a pleasure to work with and performed to the highest standards professionally and personally. I would whole heartedly recommend Greg to any of our clients without hesitation.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>Tom Donald</strong> ǀ Director\r\n<strong>MSC Consulting</strong>\r\n<blockquote>Vince has gained a reputation for both the quality and accuracy of his advice for difficult and complex civils and infrastructure projects. I would have no hesitation in recommending Vince to any client organisation that requires commercial and cost advice of the highest level.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>Tony Webb</strong> ǀ Director\r\n<strong>Pragmatix Limited</strong>\r\n<blockquote>Greg’s previous experience as a contractor gives him extra insight into project costs which has been invaluable.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>Alan Blyde</strong> ǀ Principal, Wellington Manager\r\n<strong>Harrison Grierson Consultants</strong>\r\n<blockquote>Vince, with his many years of civil quantity surveying experience, was instrumental in providing sound cost planning advice as Auckland Airport undertook a review of our long term development plans in The Landing (a 120 hectare precinct). In addition his cost estimating and reporting abilities during the development of the detailed design of the next 10 hectare (net developable area) expansion within the precinct was invaluable in advance of getting approval to expend funds on the project. In a challenging and uncertain civil construction environment Vince’s input helped to ensure that there were no cost surprises when it came time to tender the project.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>\r\nDonavin Wick</strong> ǀ Property Project Manager\r\n<strong>Auckland International Airport Limited</strong>\r\n<blockquote>Greg provided a professional level of service to CentrePort and is thorough, knowledgeable and great to work with.</blockquote>\r\n<strong>\r\nBrenda Boughen</strong>\r\n<strong>CentrePort Property</strong>', 'Testimonials', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'testimonials', '', '', '2014-10-25 04:20:42', '2014-10-25 04:20:42', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/access/?page_id=228', 0, 'page', '', 0),
