(309, 1, '2014-07-22 00:43:41', '2014-07-22 00:43:41', '[two_third_last]\r\n<div style="height: 150px; margin-left: 0px; margin-top: -98px; margin-bottom: 55px; z-index: 0; width: 976px;">\r\n<div style="margin-top: -21px; height: 80px;">\r\n<div style="float: left; font-size: 36px; color: #fff; text-shadow: 1px 1px 0px #000;">PROJECTS</div>\r\n<div style="float: right; font-size: 15px; color: #fff; text-shadow: 1px 1px 0px #000; width: 60%; text-align: right;">DALDY &amp; HASLEY STREETS</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="margin-top: -21px;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[two_third]\r\n<h3 style="margin-bottom: 40px; font-family: Arial; margin-top: 30px; color: #530c2e;">DALDY &amp; HASLEY STREETS</h3>\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 250px; padding-bottom: 25px;">Client :</td>\r\n<td style="padding-bottom: 25px;">Auckland Waterfront Development Agency</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 250px;">Services Provided :</td>\r\n<td>-  Concept Estimates</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 250px;"></td>\r\n<td>-  Developed Design Estimate</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 250px;"></td>\r\n<td>-  Detailed Design Estimate and Tender Schedules</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 250px;"></td>\r\n<td>-  Post Contract Cost Management\r\nProduction of monthly financial reports, payment recommendations, variations, final accounts, etc</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe upgrade of Daldy and Hasley Streets in the Wynyard Quarter providing a new urban landscape linking the Quarter to Fanshawe Street, Victoria Park and the CBD. Daldy Street incorporates a linear park which includes lawns, pathways, ‘water’ play areas, feature tanks, rain gardens and a variety of other recreational spaces.\r\n\r\nThe upgrade of Daldy and Hasley Streets in the Wynyard Quarter providing a new urban landscape linking the Quarter to Fanshawe Street, Victoria Park and the CBD. Daldy Street incorporates a linear park which includes lawns, pathways, ‘water’ play areas, feature tanks, rain gardens and a variety of other recreational spaces.\r\n\r\nThe upgrade of Daldy and Hasley Streets in the Wynyard Quarter providing a new urban landscape linking the Quarter to Fanshawe Street, Victoria Park and the CBD. Daldy Street incorporates a linear park which includes lawns, pathways, ‘water’ play areas, feature tanks, rain gardens and a variety of other recreational spaces.\r\n\r\n[/two_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last]<img class="alignleft  wp-image-335" src="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/Screen-Shot-2014-07-22-at-12.41.25-pm.png" alt="Screen Shot 2014-07-22 at 12.41.25 pm" width="418" height="475" />[/one_third_last]', 'DALDY & HASLEY STREETS', '', 'draft', 'open', 'closed', '', 'daldy-hasley-streets', '', '', '2014-10-25 03:40:34', '2014-10-25 03:40:34', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/access/?page_id=309', 0, 'page', '', 0),
