(372, 1, '2014-08-12 02:40:27', '2014-08-12 02:40:27', '<img class="alignleft wp-image-346 size-full" src="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/kean.jpg" alt="Kean Mitchell Quantity Surveyor and Cost Consultant" width="200" height="300" />\r\n\r\n<em><strong>Diploma in Building, Member NZIQS (Aff), Member ACIArb</strong></em>\r\n<em><strong> 17 Years Experience</strong></em>\r\n\r\nKean has had experience in many different roles from Project QS to Commercial Manager, Claims Consultant, Contracts and Procurement Specialist and has had experience in different industry sectors. Kean can produce pre-contract estimates, through to contract closure, and claims consultancy work, including expert witness skills, and has experience working as a PQS and for Main Contractors.\r\n\r\nKean provides costing, budget management and reporting, estimating, procurement, commercial management, risk management, contract drafting and administration services to a project. He has also worked as the Developers and Funders QS on prominent urbanisation and land development projects.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n[one_third]\r\n\r\n<b>TRANSPORT (road)\r\n</b>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>SH20 Manukau Extension</li>\r\n	<li>Canary Wharf (Cantilever Bridge)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>TRANSPORT (RAIL &amp; PT) </b>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>London Underground – Tubelines (Victoria, Bakerloo and Central)</li>\r\n	<li>New station in Manukau as part of the SH20 Manukau Extension</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>LAND DEVELOPMENT / URBANISATION</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Northgate Industrial Park, Whangarei</li>\r\n	<li>Park Avenue, North Shore</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>RESIDENTIAL DEVELOPMENTS</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regents Place London (two 9 storey blocks and 20 storey tower block) 151 units in total (50% social and key worker housing)</li>\r\n	<li>Marian Ridge Residential Development (150 units)</li>\r\n	<li>Sea View Residential Development (48 units)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n\r\n<strong>STREETSCAPES</strong>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fort Street</li>\r\n	<li>Jean Batten Place</li>\r\n	<li>Lorne Street</li>\r\n	<li>Rutland Street</li>\r\n	<li>Elliott Street</li>\r\n	<li>Darby Street</li>\r\n	<li>Commerce Street</li>\r\n	<li>Fort Lane</li>\r\n	<li>Khartoum Place</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>OFFICE / MIXED USE DEVELOPMENTS</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Regents Place (two 10 storey office buildings, 151 units)</li>\r\n	<li>Persatel Q Data (7000 m2 office and separate data centre 1200 m2)</li>\r\n	<li>5 Sinemba Crescent (1500 m2)</li>\r\n	<li>Fairbreeze Office Park (800 m2)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last]\r\n\r\n<strong>UTILITIES</strong>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>APM 3 &amp; 4 (UK), WTW, WWTW (Thames Water &amp; Southern Water)</li>\r\n	<li>Brighton &amp; Hove WWTW bid team</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<b>MARINE </b>\r\n<div class="cv">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Onehunga Foreshore Restoration</li>\r\n	<li>Hobsonville Point Launch Road</li>\r\n	<li>Westhaven Harbour Park Master Plan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>INSURANCE INDUSTRY</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Christchurch Earthquake Rebuild Programme (MWH Recovery for Vero/AAI) $4B Programme, Roles: Contracts &amp; Procurement Lead and Quantity Surveying Lead</li>\r\n	<li>Schweppes Cadburys – Pontefract (£70M rebuild of the Confectionary Factory which was destroyed by fire)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n[/one_third_last]\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="width: 350px;" valign="top"></td>\r\n<td style="width: 450px;" valign="top"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Kean Mitchell  |  Director', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kean-mitchell', '', '', '2014-11-06 11:08:26', '2014-11-06 11:08:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/access/?page_id=372', 0, 'page', '', 0),
