(421, 1, '2014-10-03 04:22:50', '2014-10-03 04:22:50', '<div id="home_block3_inside">\r\n<h2>QUANTITY SURVEYING &amp; CONSTRUCTION COST CONSULTANCY SERVICES</h2>\r\n<h5>Our services cover the full spectrum of pre and post contract quantity surveying expertise. Some of our specialist expertise is listed below. See our full range of q<a title="Quantity Surveying Services" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/quantity-surveying-services">uantity surveying services</a></h5>\r\n[one_half]\r\n<h4>Feasibility Studies</h4>\r\nA feasibility study from Cuesko gives you accurate foundations on which to build. A robust and independent feasibility analysis is in many cases the only way to secure funding.  <a title="More about Feasibility Studies" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/services/feasibility-studies-feasibility-analysis-concept-estimates/">more details</a> [/one_half] [one_half_last]\r\n<h4>Building Life Cycle Analysis</h4>\r\nBuilding life cycle analysis, specifically building life cycle cost analysis is a growing requirement. As technology delivers improvements, clients need to understand the long term sustainability of their construction projects. <a title="Building Life Cycle Analysis" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/quantity-surveying-services/building-life-cycle-analysis/">more details </a>[/one_half_last] [one_half]\r\n<h4>Tender Documentation / Analysis</h4>\r\nEffective tendering depends on quality of tender documentation, contract conditions and engagement with the most appropriate contractors. We advise on all aspects of the process and if  need be, can administer the entire process to ensure the desired outcome. <a title="Tendering Estimates &amp; Tender  Documentation / Analysis" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/quantity-surveying-services/tendering-estimates-tender-documentation-analysis/">more details </a>[/one_half] [one_half_last]\r\n<h4>Procurement Strategy</h4>\r\nAs quantity surveyors we provide timely and strategic procurement advice and procurement management services. Understanding the contractual implications (costs and benefits) of alternative procurement strategies is an essential part of project planning and delivery.  <a title="Procurement Strategy &amp; Management" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/quantity-surveying-services/procurement-strategy/">more details</a> [/one_half_last] [one_half]\r\n<h4>Value Engineering</h4>\r\nValue engineering depends on accurate quantity surveying and value analysis; assessing the value of design in relation to costs and benefits in both form and function, to ensure the most cost effective,  desirable outcome for you.  <a title="Construction Cost Management &amp; Value Engineering" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/quantity-surveying-services/construction-cost-management/">more details</a> [/one_half] [one_half_last]\r\n<h4>Risk Management</h4>\r\nEffective risk management planning requires robust risk assessment and effective risk mitigation. As part of your construction team, we are able to quantify your risks in terms of effect, likelihood and cost and provide the strategies by which to mitigate those risks. <a title="Risk Management, Assessment &amp; Mitigation" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/quantity-surveying-services/risk-management/"> more details</a> [/one_half_last] <a class="view_all_yellow" href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/services/">View all QS Services</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clear"></div>', 'Home Block 3 - PRE AND POST CONTRACT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home-block-3-pre-and-post-contract', '', '', '2014-10-25 04:41:28', '2014-10-25 04:41:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/development/?post_type=content_block&#038;p=421', 0, 'content_block', '', 0),
(423, 1, '2014-10-03 04:23:14', '2014-10-03 04:23:14', '“When planning the delivery of Quad 5, Auckland Airport’s first speculative commercial office building in a number of years; and the headquarters of the airport’s management team, it was imperative that the end product was an outstanding facility and a financial success. John Giles, as the project Quantity Surveyor, was integral in ensuring both goals were achieved. Over the two year life of the project John was an exceptional team member who consistently delivered high quality and reliable advice and deliverables. We’d welcome the opportunity to work with John in the future.”\r\n\r\n<em>Donavin Wick, Property Project Manager Auckland International Airport Limited</em>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/testimonials/">more details</a>', 'Home Block 4 - Testimonials', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home-block-4-testimonials', '', '', '2014-10-06 01:59:08', '2014-10-06 01:59:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cuesko.co.nz/development/?post_type=content_block&#038;p=423', 0, 'content_block', '', 0),
